  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">deposit in order to fight against his country. On these and like cases it is bad to follow the law , and it is good to set aside the letter of the law and to follow the dictates of justice and the common good . This is the object of "epikeia" which we call equity. Therefore it is evident that "epikeia" is a v</data>
